name: Zatherz
tagline: Site for me and my projects
body:
### Howdy!
You've reached the website for Zatherz, the home of his projects.

### Who are you?
I'm an aspiring programmer. I program mostly in C and occasionally in C++ and Qt. I'm a developer for the future [Orbos](http://orbos.github.io/) Linux distro.

### Where all all the projects you're talking about?
Look at the sidebar on the left.
